lemma word8_and_max_simp:
  \<open>x AND 0xFF = x\<close> for x :: \<open>8 word\<close>

proof (prove)
goal (1 subgoal):
 1. x AND 255 = x

proof (prove)
using this:
  x AND mask LENGTH(8) = x

goal (1 subgoal):
 1. x AND 255 = x

proof (prove)
goal (1 subgoal):
 1. map unat enum = [0..<256]
by (simp add: enum_word_def comp_def take_bit_nat_eq_self map_idem_upt_eq)
